{"tid":183924,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日DSE 等我鼓勵下你班中學雞","createTime":"2017-04-02T12:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T13:58:25.000Z","uid":11526,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e916c2788b4c18a8619d31675d1bab799f747b3b","tid":183924,"uid":11526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"好心你地快d溫書啦 仲上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考得唔好就真係喊都無謂<br />\n你都知依家咩時勢啦 香港所有野都比大陸人入侵晒<br />\n無論大學定工作 你對大陸人分分鐘仲多過香港人<br />\n你依家再唔努力d 第時屎都無得你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好努力去考 要盡全力考好每份卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知一定有好多老師同你講 有人考得好好但最後一事無成<br />\n有人考得好差 但經過自身努力 依家創業做老細<br />\n跟手叫你唔好太着意一時成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你自己諗下啦 一百都唔知有冇一個可以鹹魚翻身<br />\n我只係知考好遲下可以做個律師 醫生做個人生勝利組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你唔係有父幹 你聽日就比心機去考"},{"pid":"15beb5b25ce60a8305af024a8e5e5775e2d3740f","tid":183924,"uid":102485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63520bcd5cdf49eae51dc71ec5d1fc86a5fcd57c","tid":183924,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:38:39.000Z","msg":"溫乜撚丫 平時有努力 聽日洗撚驚咩 訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇努力又唔係打天才波既 聽日訓喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a5c5f9b000d1be2fe3abe2cdd8b341e730a6e7","tid":183924,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:57:01.000Z","msg":"曬尻氣啦，一齊肥佬吧啦"},{"pid":"c4977d3ad1f8abf6f73c9ce164a2eba99075a2b8","tid":183924,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"搏盡無悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}